#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:63
msgid "The name of the action that will be displayed in the context menu."
msgstr "ຊື່ຂອງການປະຕິບັດການທີ່ຈະສະແດງໃນເມນູບໍລິບົດ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:76
msgid "_Description:"
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍ(_D):"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:93
msgid ""
"The description of the action that will be displayed as tooltip in the "
"statusbar when selecting the item from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳອະທິບາຍຂອງການປະຕິບັດການທີ່ຈະສະແດງເປັນ Tooltip ໃນແຖບສະຖານະ "
"ເມື່ອເລືອກລາຍການຈາກເມນູບໍລິບົດ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:106
msgid "_Submenu:"
msgstr "ເມນູຍ່ອຍ(_S):"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:123
msgid ""
"The submenu in which the action will be displayed. Leave empty for no menu. "
"Use '/' for nested menus."
msgstr ""
"ເມນູຍ່ອຍທີ່ຈະສະແດງການປະຕິບັດການ. ປ່ອຍຫວ່າງໄວ້ຖ້າບໍ່ຕ້ອງການເມນູ. ໃຊ້ '/' "
"ສຳລັບເມນູທີ່ຊ້ອນກັນ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:136
msgid "_Command:"
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງ(_C):"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:157
msgid ""
"The command (including the necessary parameters) to perform the action. See "
"the command parameter legend below for a list of supported parameter "
"variables, which will be substituted when launching the command. When upper-"
"case letters (e.g. %F, %D, %N) are used, the action will be applicable even "
"if more than one item is selected. Else the action will only be applicable "
"if exactly one item is selected."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳສັ່ງ (ລວມເຖິງພາລາມີເຕີທີ່ຈຳເປັນ) ເພື່ອປະຕິບັດການ. "
"ເບິ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍພາລາມີເຕີລຸ່ມນີ້ສຳລັບລາຍການຕົວແປທີ່ຮອງຮັບ "
"ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ເມື່ອເລີ່ມຄຳສັ່ງ. ເມື່ອໃຊ້ຕົວອັກສອນໃຫຍ່ (ເຊັ່ນ %F, %D, %N), "
"ການປະຕິບັດການຈະໃຊ້ໄດ້ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະເລືອກຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງລາຍການ. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, "
"ມັນຈະໃຊ້ໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອເລືອກພຽງລາຍການດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:172
msgid ""
"Browse the file system to select an application to use for this action."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ອງເບິ່ງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ເພື່ອເລືອກແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ສຳລັບການປະຕິບັດການນີ້."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:201
msgid "Keyboard _Shortcut:"
msgstr "ທາງລັດຄີບອດ(_S):"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:219
msgid "The keyboard shortcut for the action."
msgstr "ທາງລັດຄີບອດສຳລັບການປະຕິບັດການ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:234
msgid "Clear the keyboard shortcut for this action."
msgstr "ລ້າງຄ່າທາງລັດຄີບອດສຳລັບການປະຕິບັດການນີ້."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:263
msgid "_Icon:"
msgstr "ໄອຄອນ(_I):"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:283
msgid ""
"Click this button to select an icon file that will be displayed in the "
"context menu in addition to the action name chosen above."
msgstr ""
"ຄລິກປຸ່ມນີ້ເພື່ອເລືອກໄຟລ໌ໄອຄອນທີ່ຈະສະແດງໃນເມນູບໍລິບົດ "
"ຄຽງຄູ່ກັບຊື່ການປະຕິບັດການທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ຂ້າງເທິງ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:294
msgid "Use Startup Notification"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນເມື່ອເລີ່ມເຮັດວຽກ"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:298
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you want a waiting cursor to be shown while the action"
" is launched. This is also highly recommended if you have focus stealing "
"prevention enabled in your window manager."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຖ້າເຈົ້າຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ສະແດງເຄີເຊີການລໍຖ້າໃນຂະນະທີ່ເລີ່ມການປະຕິບັດການ."
" ແນະນຳຢ່າງຍິ່ງຖ້າເຈົ້າເປີດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນການຍາດຈຸດໂຟກັສ (focus stealing "
"prevention) ໃນຕົວຈັດການໜ້າຕ່າງ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:351
msgid ""
"The following command parameters will be substituted when launching the "
"action:"
msgstr "ພາລາມີເຕີຄຳສັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ເມື່ອເລີ່ມການປະຕິບັດການ:"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:461
msgid "file name of the selected file"
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:477
msgid "file names of all selected files"
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງທຸກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:492
msgid "path of the selected file's directory"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:507
msgid "paths of all selected files' directories"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີຂອງທຸກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:522
msgid "path of the selected file including the file name"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ ລວມເຖິງຊື່ໄຟລ໌"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:537
msgid "paths of all selected files including the file names"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງທຸກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ ລວມເຖິງຊື່ໄຟລ໌"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:609
msgid "Basic"
msgstr "ພື້ນຖານ"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:627
msgid "_File Pattern:"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌(_F):"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:644
msgid ""
"Enter a list of patterns that will be used to determine whether this action "
"should be displayed for a selected file. If you specify more than one "
"pattern here, the list items must be separated with semicolons (e.g. "
"*.txt;*.doc)."
msgstr ""
"ປ້ອນລາຍການຮູບແບບທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ກຳນົດວ່າຄວນສະແດງການປະຕິບັດການນີ້ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກບໍ່."
" ຖ້າເຈົ້າລະບຸຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງຮູບແບບ, ໃຫ້ຂັ້ນດ້ວຍຈ້ຳຈຸດ (ເຊັ່ນ *.txt;*.doc)."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:647
#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:678
msgid "*"
msgstr "*"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:658
msgid "_Range (min-max):"
msgstr "ຊ່ວງ (ຕ່ຳສຸດ-ສູງສຸດ)(_R):"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:675
msgid ""
"If the command should operate on say two or three files, enter the numerical"
" range 2-3. If there are no limits, this string should be empty."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຄຳສັ່ງຄວນເຮັດວຽກກັບສອງ ຫຼື ສາມໄຟລ໌, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຕົວເລກເປັນ 2-3. "
"ຖ້າບໍ່ມີການຈຳກັດ, ໃຫ້ປ່ອຍຫວ່າງໄວ້."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:689
msgid "Appears if selection contains:"
msgstr "ປາກົດຂຶ້ນຖ້າສິ່ງທີ່ເລືອກປະກອບດ້ວຍ:"

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-editor.ui:709
