msgstr "ລຶບການປະຕິບັດການທີ່ເລືອກຢູ່."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-chooser.ui:115
msgid "Move the currently selected action up by one row."
msgstr "ຍ້າຍການປະຕິບັດການທີ່ເລືອກຂຶ້ນໜຶ່ງແຖວ."

#: plugins/thunar-uca/thunar-uca-chooser.ui:124
msgid "Move the currently selected action down by one row."
msgstr "ຍ້າຍການປະຕິບັດການທີ່ເລືອກລົງໜຶ່ງແຖວ."

